your political stripe remind you
that we're

41:03.628 --> 41:05.863 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
talking about just ordinary
human beings.

41:05.897 --> 41:08.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SREENIVASAN: Anne Barnard of
"The New York
